name: Proto Labs, Inc.
description: Proto Labs, Inc. is a leading provider of digital manufacturing services, specializing in rapid prototyping and low-volume production. Founded in 1999, the company has revolutionized the way manufacturers create prototypes and production parts using advanced technologies such as 3D printing, CNC machining, and injection molding. Proto Labs offers a platform that allows engineers and designers to upload their 3D CAD models and receive instant quotes, enabling faster product development cycles. The company serves a diverse range of industries including aerospace, medical, automotive, and consumer products, helping clients bring their innovations to market quickly and efficiently. With a commitment to quality and precision, Proto Labs employs stringent quality control measures and maintains certifications such as ISO 9001 and AS9100. The company’s mission is to empower innovators by providing them with the tools and resources needed to transform their ideas into tangible products. Proto Labs continues to invest in technology and automation, expanding its capabilities to meet the evolving needs of its customers in the digital manufacturing landscape.
